This paper proposes a protocol for secure communication in IoT systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses key delegation and access control, which are topics related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper mentions the decoupled communication model typical of IoT systems, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE).
